<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Simon is my best friend in school.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西蒙是我在学校最好的朋友。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200812/0b63edc6e5c146a0a7212a61abcdb1bb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Alex is my best friend in the park.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">亚历克斯是我在公园最好的朋友。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200812/7c6913a0065046a0aad23db4712d899c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Drew is my best friend at the pool.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">德鲁是我在泳池最好的朋友。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200812/f7ff6b9f75a24e62a88b89926df4b5ab.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Lee is my best friend at T-ball games.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李是我在网球比赛中最好的朋友。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200812/8d53477daf5444d7ad1221faacb13f6b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>My best friend at services is Jim.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我在项目服务方面最好的朋友是吉姆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200812/a64d86f477ba46b2b4e0b660f08a12de.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Ellen is my best neighborhood friend.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">艾伦是我最好的邻居朋友。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200812/ea583d31a781492d9ed5bda6146f0d30.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>My best friend in dance class is Kim.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我在舞蹈课上最好的朋友是金姆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200812/6e26eb0f8ceb4c3c8ee144933bb7496f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Becca is my best “summer cabin” friend</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贝卡是我最好的“夏日小屋”的朋友。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200812/709c12185a2c4bd88ed98d9831f80947.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>At home,my best friend is Gram.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在家里，我最好的朋友是格兰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200812/940792f08c214b24968ff91173b16bdb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>I am very, very lucky—I have a best friend wherever I am!</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我非常非常的幸运，无论我在哪里，我都有一个最好的朋友。</p>